OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FA major report into maternity care has
OL,7,Ffound repeated failures in NHS
OL,8,Fservices that have left families
OL,9,Fsuffering, highlighting incidences of
OL,10,Fsystemic racism and unsafe maternity
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FThe final report and recommendations
OL,14,Fof the Independent National Maternity
OL,15,Fand Neonatal Investigation, led by
OL,16,FBaroness Valerie Amos, was published
OL,17,Fon Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FThe investigation spoke to 450
OL,7,Ffamilies and 12 NHS trusts about the
OL,8,F"mistakes and inequalities" in
OL,9,Fmaternity and neonatal care, and
OL,10,Fconcluded a need for "urgent reform".
OL,12,FIt raised grave concerns around those
OL,13,Fgiving birth "not being listened to,
OL,14,Fheard or believed", with "serious
OL,15,Fconsequences for the safety and
OL,16,Fquality of care they receive".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FAfter reading the report's conclusion
OL,7,Fthat families have suffered from
OL,8,Frepeated failures in NHS care, the
OL,9,Fgovernment has agreed to appoint a
OL,10,Fnational maternity commissioner to
OL,11,Fdrive change.
OL,13,FAmos said the new maternity
OL,14,Fcommissioner must be accountable to
OL,15,FParliament and have a "relentless
OL,16,Ffocus on improving maternity and
OL,17,Fneonatal care", with the aim of
OL,18,Fredesigning the service.
OL,26,@wD@WOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
