PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FThis includes "clear minimum national
OL,7,Fstandards for safety and putting in
OL,8,Fplace effective governance and
OL,9,Faccountability."
OL,11,FAdditionally, the report found that
OL,12,Fservices "are not designed in a way
OL,13,Fthat ensures consistent safety", with
OL,14,Fsome patients stating that they had
OL,15,F"not been able to give informed
OL,16,Fconsent to medical procedures, due to
OL,17,Fpoor communication and lack of
OL,18,Finformation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FOverall, the impact of "medical
OL,7,Fmisogyny" was found throughout,
OL,8,F"leading to an embedded culture in
OL,9,Fwhich women's voices are ignored".
OL,11,FThe report also concluded that racism
OL,12,Fand structural inequalities are
OL,13,F"embedded throughout the maternity and
OL,14,Fneonatal system, with profound
OL,15,Fimplications for outcomes and the
OL,16,Fquality of care women and babies
OL,17,Freceive".
OL,26,@qD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
