PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FPatients told of instances of
OL,7,Fdiscrimination, including "receiving
OL,8,Funfair or unequal treatment, leading
OL,9,Fto delays, unsafe care with, at times,
OL,10,Fdevastating outcomes."
OL,12,FSome also noted stereotyping and
OL,13,Fracial slurs on NHS wards,
OL,14,FIslamophobia and antisemitism. One
OL,15,FMuslim patient was asked, "why are you
OL,16,Fwearing this?" while a Jewish patient
OL,17,Fwas told that "Jewish people are
OL,18,Fsneaky".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FFurther to this, the report raises
OL,7,Fconcerns about the treatment of staff
OL,8,Fworking in the maternity sector.
OL,10,FAccording to the review, staff also
OL,11,Fexperienced racism, "both from other
OL,12,Fstaff and from women, birthing people
OL,13,Fand families".
OL,15,FThey told of working in poor-quality
OL,16,Fand sometimes dangerous clinical
OL,17,Fenvironments, "often working long
OL,18,Fshifts without breaks, in areas
OL,19,Flacking appropriate spaces" for rest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FAmos has said that families should
OL,7,Fhave the right to an independent
OL,8,Finvestigation of their care when
OL,9,Fthings go wrong, and they do not agree
OL,10,Fwith the findings of internal NHS
OL,11,Freviews.
OL,13,FFamilies who tried to get answers when
OL,14,Fharm occurred felt that internal
OL,15,Finvestigation teams were "marking
OL,16,Ftheir own homework", the report found.
OL,18,FThere were also noted instances of "no
OL,19,Finvestigation or review" being
OL,20,Fundertaken "because staff judged there
OL,21,Fto be no errors in the care provided".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FThe report comes less than a week
OL,7,Fafter an inquiry into Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust (NUH),
OL,9,Fled by senior midwife Donna Ockenden,
OL,10,Ffound more than 500 mothers and babies
OL,11,Fsuffered avoidable harm or died due to
OL,12,F"deeply embedded systemic failures" at
OL,13,Fthe "toxic" hospital trust.
OL,15,FAmos described hearing about
OL,16,F"heartbreaking cases" and said the
OL,17,F"emotional toll and cost to families
OL,18,Fis indescribable".
OL,26,@uD@KO]zD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FShe added: "Women, babies and families
OL,7,Fdeserve maternity and neonatal care
OL,8,Fthat is safe, compassionate and
OL,9,Fequitable wherever they live".
OL,11,FThe report said NHS trust boards must
OL,12,Fhave clear oversight of how patients
OL,13,Fare triaged for care, including
OL,14,Fregular reviews of waiting times and
OL,15,Fperformance.
OL,26,@nD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FWithin a year, there should also be a
OL,7,Fnational standard brought in for what
OL,8,Fgood triage looks like, and all
OL,9,Fmaternity units must also have
OL,10,Fdedicated triage staff, who are all
OL,11,Ftrained in rapid assessment.
OL,13,FThe report further said the government
OL,14,Fand regulators such as the General
OL,15,FMedical Council (GMC) and the Nursing
OL,16,Fand Midwifery Council (NMC) must
OL,17,F"treat racism, discrimination and
OL,18,Finequality as a critical maternity
OL,19,Fsafety issue".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
