PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHealth Secretary, James Murray, said:
OL,12,F"For too long, women, babies and
OL,13,Ffamilies have been failed by a system
OL,14,Fthat didn't listen. Their stories are
OL,15,Fheartbreaking and demand action.
OL,17,F"Appointing the UK's first ever
OL,18,Fmaternity and neonatal commissioner
OL,19,Fwill drive lasting change and make
OL,20,Fsure women and families are never
OL,21,Fignored again".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782886684
OL,3,CMaternity review: 'Urgent reform'
OL,4,Cneeded to tackle repeated NHS failings
OL,6,FThe Government also committed to
OL,7,Frolling out a national perinatal
OL,8,Fequity and anti-discrimination
OL,9,Fprogramme.
OL,11,FSome 1,000 temporary roles will also
OL,12,Fbe created to help newly-qualified
OL,13,Fmidwives join the NHS, backed by more
OL,14,Fthan #10 million in funding.
OL,16,FThe Birth Trauma Association said the
OL,17,FAmos review was "disappointing for
OL,18,Ffamilies" and a "huge missed
OL,19,Fopportunity".
OL,26,@yD@QOUzD@IO]zD@QOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
